|-
|velar||&lt;big&gt;ක&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ka}})||&lt;big&gt;ඛ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|kha}})||&lt;big&gt;ග&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ga}})||&lt;big&gt;ඝ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|gha}})||&lt;big&gt;ඞ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ṅa}})
|-
|palatal||&lt;big&gt;ච&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ca}})||&lt;big&gt;ඡ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|cha}})||&lt;big&gt;ජ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ja}})||&lt;big&gt;ඣ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|jha}})||&lt;big&gt;ඤ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ña}})
