|retroflex||&lt;big&gt;ට&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ṭa}})||&lt;big&gt;ඨ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ṭha}})||&lt;big&gt;ඩ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ḍa}})||&lt;big&gt;ඪ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ḍha}})||&lt;big&gt;ණ&lt;/big&gt; ({{IAST|ṇa}})
